HEADWORD: Pugilism
<hw>Pu"gil*ism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>pugil</ets> a pugilist, boxer, akin to <ets>pugnus</ets> the fist.
Cf. <er>Pugnacious</er>, <er>Fist</er>.]</ety> <def>The practice of
boxing, or fighting with the fist.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

